    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it's that perfect! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and strictly maintained. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
