    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines what it means to be 'like-new.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its factory-original luster. The exterior paint is flawless, devoid of any stone chips or swirl marks, and has been protected with a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented from day one. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is the finest example currently on the market. Sale includes all original keys, manuals, and a bespoke car cover.",
