      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is in pristine, mint condition! I\u2019ve honestly babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you want a 'new' car experience without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
